### Which @angular/* package(s) are the source of the bug?

core

### Is this a regression?

Yes

### Description

Suppose I have the below template - 

```
@if (numbers().length > 0) {
    @for (number of numbers; track number.name) {
      <some-card [value]="number"></some-card>
    }
 }
@if (digits().length > 0) {
    @for (digit of digits; track digit.name) {
      <some-card [value]="digit"></some-card>
    }
 }
```

The order of the `some-card` element received from viewChildren have elements from digits before elements from numbers in the resulting list.


